Package org.apache.commons.imaging.color

Class ColorHunterLab

java.lang.Object
org.apache.commons.imaging.color.ColorHunterLab
public final class ColorHunterLab extends Object
Represents a color in the Hunter Lab color space.

Contains the constant values for black, white, red, green, and blue.

Since:
1.0-alpha1
See Also:
